<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>كَالنِّكَاحِ وَالْبَيْعِ وَالْهِبَةِ وَالرَّهْنِ، وَكَالْوَقْفِ عِنْدَ الْجُمْهُورِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الثَّانِي:</span> مَا هُوَ مُؤَقَّتٌ لاَ يَقْبَل التَّأْبِيدَ كَالإِْجَارَةِ وَالْمُزَارَعَةِ وَالْمُسَاقَاةِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَالثَّالِثُ:</span> مَا هُوَ قَابِلٌ لِلتَّوْقِيتِ وَالتَّأْبِيدِ كَالْكَفَالَةِ. <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَانْظُرْ لِلتَّفْصِيل مُصْطَلَحَ <span class="c2">(تَأْقِيتٍ)</span> وَانْظُرْ أَيْضًا <span class="c2">(بَيْعٌ. هِبَةٌ. إِجَارَةٌ. إِلَخْ)</span> .<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>تَأْبِينٌ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">اُنْظُرْ:</span> رِثَاءٌ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>تَأْجِيلٌ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">اُنْظُرْ:</span> أَجَلٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>تَأَخُّرٌ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">اُنْظُرْ:</span> تَأْخِيرٌ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
